Message.En: Materials for Out of Stock Goods

There are many injured people, so medicine
sells out quickly. Especially, medicine made
from <LQIM> 
requires <LQVA> to make, and
everyone wants it, so we can't keep up!
Yes, we're out of stock again.

ケガをしてる人が多いから、薬がすぐ売り切れちゃうわ
特に<LQIM>を<LQVA>個使って作った薬はみんな欲しがるから、作っても作ってもきりがなくって！
ええ、もちろん今も品切れよ
